<Docs title="VFS Path System">
  <p>
    rdc-cli exposes all capture data through a virtual filesystem (VFS). Every
    draw call, resource, pipeline state, and shader is accessible via a stable
    path. This makes it easy to browse, script, and integrate with tools.
  </p>

